 2022-02502022-03-09,  ,  ,  DND, 
ActNational Defence Act
SubjectOrder authorizing the delivery of non-surplus materials to Ukraine
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of National Defence to deliver non-surplus Canadian Armed Forces materials and equipment, valued up to $75 million dollars, to the Public Services and Procurement Canada for disposal to Ukraine in order to support its armed forces during the ongoing Russian invasion.
